headline: Dividend King Federal Realty Has a High Yield and Industry-Leading Business
summary: Federal Realty has the longest dividend increase streak in the REIT sector.  Federal Realty's dividend yield is notably higher than the REIT industry average.  Federal Realty (NYSE: FRT) is not the largest real estate investment trust (REIT) you can buy.
